Package Responsibility and Collaboration
========================================

* paxos
    + .NewInstance
    + .learn
    + .accept
    + .coordinate
    + Node
    + msg(s)
* proto
    + .Encode(parts ... interface{})
    + .Decode
* router
    ^ paxos (instances)
    + .Route
    + Msg
* mgmt (aka extra shit that we don't know where it goes)
    ^ auth
    + applying paxos outputs to the data store
    + becoming the leader
    + learning about any other leader there might be
    + adding/removing acceptors/learners
    + fault detection
* auth
    ^ sasl (??)
    + .Auth
* borg
    ^ tls (??)
    ^ net
    ^ proto
    ^ router (use Msg)
    ^ mgmt
    + .ListenAndServe
* borgd (cli)
    + borg
